            "value": "Zend_Form_Element_Hidden elements should render outside of general form elements; either directly after the form opening tag, or before the form closing tag:\r\n\r\n<form action=\"make-coffee\" ... >\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"coffeeDrinkerId\" \/>\r\n<ul>\r\n   <li><label ...etc\r\n\r\nIt should also not have decorators like labels or errors."
