                    },
                    "body": "Small further to Jordan's comment: the parent block element should be able to wrap multiple hidden input fields to avoid extraneous markup like:\n\n<div>\n    <input type=\"hidden\" ... \/>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n    <input type=\"hidden\" ... \/>\n<\/div>",
