                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I think this is a good idea, but the logistics to get it working are pretty hairy currently. I've added a test in r8689 to cover the desired functionality, but marked it as incomplete; I'll revisit after the 1.5.0 release.\n\nIn the meantime, you can group hidden elements inside a display group or even a sub form pretty easily, and provide decorators that will hide the entire group; I suggest doing this until I can work on the functionality.",
